Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.92,0:22:09.22,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\t(0,480,\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HF59F1B&)\fad(0,200)}將喜歡與討厭拋諸腦後
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.68,0:22:15.56,EDCN,,0,0,0,,一聲令下 世界紛紛擾擾
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.45,0:22:28.07,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an1\3c&H1BBFD9&}將石塊擲向天際
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.07,0:22:29.74,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an1\3c&H1BBFD9&}不期而至 今日晴空萬里
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.74,0:22:32.08,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an1\3c&H1BBFD9&\fad(0,200)}所有煩惱煙消雲散
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.87,0:22:38.92,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\3c&H0608A3&\fad(0,200)}隨著鐘聲響起 地球不斷旋轉
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.79,0:22:41.25,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\3c&HBD7AA1&}窗簾輕輕搖曳
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.25,0:22:43.09,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\3c&HBD7AA1&}敞開教科書的文字上
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.09,0:22:46.30,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\3c&HBD7AA1&}字裡行間彷彿隨心起舞
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.30,0:22:49.76,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\3c&HA82DE4&}踏著步伐走進夢境
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.76,0:22:53.10,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\3c&HA82DE4&}一躍而起
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.10,0:22:58.27,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an1\3c&HC593AF&\pos(150,1000)}未來並非早已注定
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.27,0:23:00.02,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(1150,1000)\3c&H1C86E5&}璀璨的祈願
Dialogue: 1,0:23:00.02,0:23:01.61,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(1150,1000)\3c&H1C86E5&}不論何種希望
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.61,0:23:04.02,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(1150,1000)\3c&H1C86E5&}都定能被緊握
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.02,0:23:06.28,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(474,1000)\3c&H0F10D6&}現在 抬起頭來
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.28,0:23:09.78,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(474,1000)\3c&H0F10D6&}將喜歡與討厭拋諸腦後
Dialogue: 1,0:23:09.78,0:23:13.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H624356&\an9}唱反調 再顛倒 Get you
Dialogue: 1,0:23:13.12,0:23:16.25,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H624356&\an9}觸手可及之處 炙熱融化般的思念
Dialogue: 1,0:23:16.25,0:23:19.75,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H624356&\an9}將其釋放 在心中描繪彩虹
Dialogue: 1,0:23:19.75,0:23:23.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an9\3c&H024E9C&}喜歡與討厭亦是成長的痛
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.00,0:23:26.26,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an9\3c&H024E9C&}走投無路 也沒關係
Dialogue: 1,0:23:26.26,0:23:29.68,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an1\3c&H8A00A9&\pos(1210,1000)}是你讓我陷入迷醉
Dialogue: 1,0:23:29.68,0:23:33.10,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an1\3c&H8A00A9&\pos(1080,1060)}將無可挽回的歲月 刻畫在心頭吧
