Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:05.68,Screen,,0,0,0,,{=4}{\fscy90.66\fscx90.66\fn方正标准大黑_GBK\bord3\1a&HFF&\pos(959.02,256.87)}將喜歡與討厭拋諸腦後
