Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:05.81,Screen,,0,0,0,,{=4}{\fscy90.49\fscx90.49\fn方正标准大黑_GBK\bord3\1a&HFF&\pos(959,257.45)}將喜歡與討厭拋諸腦後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:05.85,Screen,,0,0,0,,{=4}{\fscy90.47\fscx90.47\fn方正标准大黑_GBK\bord3\1a&HFF&\pos(959,257.59)}將喜歡與討厭拋諸腦後
